title: Top Places to visit in Mahbubnagar, Telangana
content: Mahbub Nagar is a city in Mahbubnagar District of the Indian state of Telangana named after the 6th Nizam, Mir Mahbub Ali Khan. It is the headquarters of Mahbub Nagar mandal in Mahbub Nagar revenue division. The city is also the largest in the district with an area of 39.64 km2 (15.31 sq mi) and
